1. **human_ppi.json** - Configuration for human PPI networks

{
  "net_names": [
    "bionic/inputs/Hein-2015.txt",
    "bionic/inputs/Huttlin-2015.txt",
    "bionic/inputs/Huttlin-2017.txt",
    "bionic/inputs/Rolland-2014.txt"
  ],
  "out_name": "bionic/outputs/human_ppi",
  "epochs": 2123,
  "batch_size": 2048,
  "learning_rate": 0.0005830944755717023,
  "gat_shapes": {
    "dimension": 68,
    "n_heads": 10,
    "n_layers": 3
  },
  "embedding_size": 512,
  "save_model": false
}

   - Uses 4 input datasets (Hein-2015, Huttlin-2015, Huttlin-2017, Rolland-2014)
   - Trains for 2,123 epochs with batch size 2,048
   - Uses a Graph Attention Network (GAT) with 68-dimensional embeddings, 10 attention heads, and 3 layers
   - 512-dimensional final embeddings

