4. **yeast_gi_coex_ppi_tensorboard.json** - TensorBoard-enabled variant of the yeast configuration
{
  "net_names": [
    "bionic/inputs/Costanzo-2016.txt",
    "bionic/inputs/Hu-2007.txt",
    "bionic/inputs/Krogan-2006.txt"
  ],
  "out_name": "bionic/outputs/yeast_gi_coex_ppi",
  "epochs": 2123,
  "batch_size": 2048,
  "learning_rate": 0.0005830944755717023,
